\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:12;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"https://wpdeveloper.net/?p=498135\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:484:\"<p>Embed Instagram Feed on WordPress without any coding just with 1-click using EmbedPress. It lets you embed more 75+ source links instead of it on your favorite editor Gutenberg, Classic editor, or Elementor page builder. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/embed-instagram-feed-on-wordpress/\">How to Embed Instagram Feed on WordPress Using EmbedPress For Free</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net\">WPDeveloper</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Afrin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8282:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Are you looking for a perfect solution to<strong> <a href=\"https://embedpress.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">embed Instagram feed</a> </strong>on WordPress </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">automatically without adding any codes? We are here to help you out with the easiest solution that lets you embed anything. It will embed any type of the link instantly on any of your favorite editor </span><b>Gutenberg, Classic Editor, or Elementor</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> for absolutely free. Want to know in detail? Let’s get started!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Introducing </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https://embedpress.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">EmbedPress</a>: ultimate embedding solution for WordPress</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> that will help you out to embed from more 75+ source links. Now you can easily embed anything and everything just within 1-click, and boost your site engagement with interactive content. </span></p>\n<p><span id=\"more-498135\"></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/How-to-Embed-Instagram-Feed-on-WordPress-Without-Any-Coding.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-498154\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/How-to-Embed-Instagram-Feed-on-WordPress-Without-Any-Coding.png\" alt=\"embed Instagram feed on WordPress\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/How-to-Embed-Instagram-Feed-on-WordPress-Without-Any-Coding.png 1280w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/How-to-Embed-Instagram-Feed-on-WordPress-Without-Any-Coding-600x338.png 600w, https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/How-to-Embed-Instagram-Feed-on-WordPress-Without-Any-Coding-768x432.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Instagram<b> </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">is one of those popular social channels for individuals or for businesses. It helps you to do strategic social media marketing with its amazing visual content. People get attracted and engage more because of its variety of content. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">That’s why </span><b>Instagram feed </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">can be a way to boost site traffic and engagement. All you have to do is to find a perfect way that can showcase your Insta feed amazing content on the website instantly and influence your visitors to go through your whole website without any hassle.  </span></p>\n<p><b><i>Note: You need to install and activate</i></b><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/embedpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"> <b><i>EmbedPress Plugin</i></b></a><b><i> to embed Instagram on your WordPress site.</i></b></p>\n<p><iframe title=\"How to Embed Instagram Images in WordPress\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/h8oPwlZ9P5A?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>If you have successfully installed the plugin, then you are ready to embed anything including Instagram on your WordPress site.</p>\n<h2><b>How To Embed Instagram Feed On WordPress Using EmbedPress</b></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can embed links for more than </span><b>75+ sources anytime you want with EmbedPress </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">just within a click. It helps you to embed any images, videos, GIFs, posts, audio clips, maps, and many more except Instagram feed. Let\'s check out the step by step guideline below to know how to </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">embed Instagram feed on WordPress using EmbedPress</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: </span></p>\n<h3><b>Pick Gutenberg Editor To Embed Instagram Feed Instantly</b></h3>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Step 1:</strong> You just have to copy the link of your desired Instagram post and insert it on the Gutenberg editor.</span></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/iGKGxPg2m9.gif\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-498148\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/iGKGxPg2m9.gif\" alt=\"embed Instagram feed on WordPress\" width=\"1353\" height=\"457\" /></a></p>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Step 2:</strong> </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Afterward, It will automatically fetch and display your feed outstandingly without any coding.</span></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/mpRHiYtFBJ.gif\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-498150\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/mpRHiYtFBJ.gif\" alt=\"embed Instagram feed on WordPress\" width=\"1350\" height=\"541\" /></a></p>\n<h3><b>Embedding Instagram Feed on Classic Editor </b></h3>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Step 1:</strong> </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Similarly for Classic Editor, you have to get the exact link of your most viewed or any Instagram posts that you want to embed and insert it on the editorial panel. </span></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/ghFgFsGLp8.gif\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-498146\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/ghFgFsGLp8.gif\" alt=\"embed Instagram feed on WordPress\" width=\"1342\" height=\"515\" /></a></p>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><strong>Step 2: </strong>Later, </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It will then automatically fetch and embed the Instagram feed on your website just with 1 click.</span></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/LjdnD5uhG1-1.gif\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-498147\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/LjdnD5uhG1-1.gif\" alt=\"embed Instagram feed on WordPress\" width=\"1349\" height=\"508\" /></a></p>\n<h3><b>Embed Instagram Feed On </b><b>Elementor</b></h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To start embedding your desired </span><b>Instagram feed </b>content on Elementor site<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, you have to follow some steps that are mentioned below:</span></p>\n<h4><b>Step 1: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You have to find out the EmbedPress template from the Elementor &#8216;Search\' panel. You have to ‘</span><b>Drag & Drop’</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> EmbedPress element in the desired section of your Elementor site.</span></h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/EmbedPress-Image-2-2.gif\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-498141\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/EmbedPress-Image-2-2.gif\" alt=\"embed Instagram feed on WordPress\" width=\"1366\" height=\"576\" /></a></p>\n<h4><b>Step 2: </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Afterward, You just have to copy and paste the link of your desire content on the </span><b>&#8216;Embedded Link\'</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> panel. Then it will automatically track and publish your content just the way it is.</span><a href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/oqZEmxxk6T.gif\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-498142\" src=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/oqZEmxxk6T.gif\" alt=\"embed Instagram feed on WordPress\" width=\"1350\" height=\"580\" /></a></h4>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Embedding any type of content from different sources without any coding could not be easier.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> With EmbedPress, you can now automatically showcase the content interactively on your website without any hassle just with a few clicks. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you find this blog helpful, you can share your opinion by commenting below. And if you have not used <a title=\"EmbedPress\" href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/plugins/embedpress/\">EmbedPress</a> </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">yet, get started right now.</span></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net/embed-instagram-feed-on-wordpress/\">How to Embed Instagram Feed on WordPress Using EmbedPress For Free</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpdeveloper.net\">WPDeveloper</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;