(374, 1, '2020-08-04 05:08:43', '2020-08-04 05:08:43', 'Have you ever need help \n				<noscript>\n					in writing essay, to make your argument looks smart, to make sure your pets understand you, to point out other\'s mistake because you simply hate them				</noscript>\n					 ?\n			<!-- close .eael-fancy-text-container -->\n			<h1>We are here to help </h1>		\n			<h2> you.</h2>		\n			<h2>Grammar Na*i will be your reliable Kamerad.</h2>		\n			<h1>Why Grammar Na*zi?</h1>		\n			<p>Our mission is to help our users seem educated (especially on the internet) by having grammar-error free content.<br><br>\nGrammar Na*i does more than grammar, spelling, and punctuation checking. We also help you to choose your words. Why? With the right choice of words, you\'d look even smarter!<br><br>\nOther than that, we can also help you with some translations.</p>		\n			But you have to pay more of course :)		\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"222\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Your-removebg-preview-300x222.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Your-removebg-preview-300x222.png 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Your-removebg-preview-e1596302378772.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />											\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"231\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Youre-removebg-preview-300x231.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Youre-removebg-preview-300x231.png 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Youre-removebg-preview.png 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />											\n			<h1>10,000++ Languages</h1>		\n			<p>Unity in diversity!<br>\nDid you know there are roughly 6,500 languages spoken by human in this world?<br>\nMaybe now you wonder how can Grammar Na*i supports more than 10,000 languages? That\'s impossible!<br>\nNote this: Nothing is impossible!<br>Because...</p>		\n			<h1>Grammar Na*i also supports animal languages!</h1>		\n			<p>In need of sharing your thoughts but only have your cats around?<br>\nWant to tell your dogs that they are adopted?<br>\nEver wonder how does it feel to be locked in a zoo?<br>\nOr maybe you just want to have a little chat with the stray cat you found on your way home?<br>\nNow everything is possible with Grammar Na*i!</p>		\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"135\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/mweo-300x135.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/mweo-300x135.png 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/mweo-1024x462.png 1024w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/mweo-768x346.png 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/mweo.png 1146w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />											\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"216\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/meow-300x216.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/meow-300x216.png 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/meow-768x554.png 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/meow.png 914w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />											\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"187\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/lol-300x187.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/lol-300x187.png 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/lol.png 498w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />											\n			<h1>Friendly Na*i Community</h1>		\n			<h2>Have any issues? Feel free to ask for help in Na*i Community\'s Forum!<br><br>\nYou can share LITERALLY ANYTHING there. Are you experiencing any technical issues? App bugs? Commitment issues? Existential crisis? Suicidal thoughts? Simply share it to the forum. Someone might be able to help you.<br><br>\nCommunity guidelines? Pft! We don\'t need such thing! Our community is 99% guaranteed safe for anyone. No guidlines needed.</h2>		\n			<h1>So, what are you waiting for?</h1>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Get started for free!\n					</a>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '84-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-08-04 05:08:43', '2020-08-04 05:08:43', '', 84, 'http://localhost/wordpress/2020/08/04/84-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
